JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x10C ; Turn Start Sound Index

MOVE A0 S4
JAL PlayHappyVoice 
NOP

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 5 ; Joy Animation Index
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 0 ; No loop

JAL SleepProcess ; Sleeps for 30 frames
LI A0 30

;------------------------------------------------------



exit:
LW S5 44(SP)
LW RA 76(SP)
LW S0 72(SP)
LW S1 68(SP)
LW S2 64(SP)
LW S3 60(SP)
LW S4 56(SP)
LW S6 52(SP)
LW S7 48(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80



PlayHappyVoice:
ADDIU SP SP -32
SW RA 28(SP)

LUI T1 hi(p1_char)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(p1_char) ; Load Player 1's Character address
LI T0 0x38 ; Distance between each player's Character address
MULT A0 T0 ;  Multiply Current Player Index by S3
MFLO T0 ; Move the result to S3

ADDU T1 T1 T0 ; Add result to get current Player's Character address
LBU T0 0(T1) ; Load address value into S2

ADDIU V0 T0 0x2BE ; Mario's Taunt Index

JAL PlaySound
MOVE A0 V0

LW RA 28(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 32

events.Next Space Setup:
; NAME: Next Space Setup
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Next

ADDIU SP SP -40
SW RA 36(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex
NOP

ADD A0 R0 V0 ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
ADDIU A1 R0 Next_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
ADDIU A2 R0 Next_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2

JAL SetNextChainAndSpace 
NOP


LW RA 36(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 40
events.Reverse&Next Space Setup:
; NAME: Reverse&Next Space Setup
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Reverse
; PARAM: Space|Next

ADDIU SP SP -40
SW RA 36(SP)

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; Player Index located at V0
NOP
ADD A0 R0 V0 ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
ADDIU A1 R0 Reverse_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
ADDIU A2 R0 Reverse_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2
JAL SetPrevChainAndSpace 
NOP

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; Player Index located at V0
NOP
ADD A0 R0 V0 ; Assigns Current Player Index to A0
ADDIU A1 R0 Next_chain_index ; Assigns Chain Index to A1
ADDIU A2 R0 Next_chain_space_index ; Assigns Space Index to A2
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace 
NOP

LW RA 36(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 40
